Aircraft.name: HF 12 Oblivion SMGNMA
Aircraft.Instructions:
VTOL-ing: Ac1 into VTOL mode, here the RCS is automated to keep the plane level. VTOL now controls nozzel deflecting angle. Note that to transform from hovering to level mode, you need a level speed of around 150 kn before deactivating Ac1.
Weapons: bombs & missiles are only activated via Ac2 which also opens weapon bay door. Jettison external hardpoints with Ac7.
Engines: Vector nozzles' yaw is always on, but roll and pitch depends on Ac4. Afterburner bound to Ac5.
Misc: When landed use Ac6 to open canopy and fold the wings. Flaps fixed with LandingGear. Trim always does pitch trimming. Ac3 is for a landing hook but VTOL landing should always be preferred.
Ac1-VTOL Ac2-Weapon Bay & Weapon Activation Ac3-Arresting Hook Ac4-Vector Nozzle Ac5-Afterburner Ac6-Canopy and Wing Folding Ac7-Jettison Hardpoints Ac8-Lights
